49	// Credential purge helper
50	//
51	// Called by skills:delete (all slots) and skills:upsert (removed slots only).
52	// Fetches all credentials rows and filters by ref prefix locally — fine for
53	// v1 (small N). Wrapped in try/catch at call sites so a credential hiccup
54	// never wedges a skill operation.
